         <p class="- topic/p ">Follow the procedure for how to turn off the system completely,
the off button will only turn off the rectifier, inverter and static
switch. The system is completely turned off when all the breakers
are also open. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">When the system is off there is no output voltage
and the load is not supplied. When all breakers are open the display
will also turn off.</p>
